THIS MOD WILL BE REMADE INTO A CUSTOM GAME, IF YOU HAVE ANY IMPORTANT WORLDS WITH THIS MOD REMOVE ALL PARTS FROM THIS MOD AND DISABLE IT OR THE WORLD WILL BREAK AFTER THE UPDATE!

This mod is a mistake

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Upd 1: ● Added new ecpic gamr thumbnail!!!1!
Upd 2: ● Added amogi
Upd 3: ● Added more amogi (colorful)
Upd 4: ● Fixed stats for blocks
● "dev blocks" now have background colours corresponding to their respective pfps in discord
● Amogus's default colour now correspond to effect block's defalut colour
Upd 5: ● Fixed effect block errors related to logging in and out of the world
● Added clues
Upd 6: ● Added rgb mode that turns on and off on interaction
● It's now impossible to glitch the block out and leave effect in the world without the block itself
Patch 6.1: ● Adjusted amount of amogus spawning in rgb mode so it doesn't lag out the game
● Block now resets effect color back to the color of block itself when rgb mode is turned off
● Hitbox fixes and optimisations
● Now effect changes color on paint ( turning block on and off is no longer required )
● Optimised rgb code ( giant thanks to BlueFlame )
